header: Why Chevel Shepherd's 'Voice' victory made coach Kelly Clarkson cry
description: Music star and 'The Voice' coach Kelly Clarkson choked up describing the purity and beauty of Season 15 winner Chevel Shepherd's voice.
text: The Season 15 champion, nicknamed My country Tinkerbell by her coach, Kelly Clarkson, is none other than New Mexico native Chevel Shepherd, 16. USA TODAY Chevel Shepherd, left, and her coach, Kelly Clarkson, stand on the confetti-covered stage of 'The Voice' â€¦ [+5616 chars]
